      "type": "heading",
      "id": "ubuntu-installation",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Ubuntu Installation Guide"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This guide will walk you through installing EasyGoDocs on Ubuntu."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": "requirements",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Requirements"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "Ubuntu 20.04 or later",
        "Node.js 18+",
        "pnpm or npm",
        "Git"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": "install-steps",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Install Steps"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "code": "# Clone the repository\ngit clone https://github.com/EasyGoDocs/easygodocs.git\ncd easygodocs\n\n# Install dependencies\npnpm install\n\n# Start the development server\npnpm run dev"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": "post-install",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Post-Install"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After installation, open http://localhost:3000 in your browser to access EasyGoDocs."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": "troubleshooting",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Troubleshooting"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": "common-issues",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Common Issues"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "If you encounter issues, ensure all requirements are met and dependencies are installed."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
